        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The &quot;Motor Vehicle Driver-Conductor Welfare Scheme- Sarathi Shri Award&quot; has been launched by the Transport Department, Government of Madhya Pradesh. Under this scheme, one of the state&#39;s best drivers will be honored with the &quot;Sarathi Shri&quot; award, which includes a cash prize, a certificate of appreciation, and a trophy. The state government will present this award at a special ceremony. \n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "**Award Components**\n\n- Cash Prize: ₹1,00,000/-\n- Appreciation Certificate\n- Trophy\n\n<br>\n\n",
