          "process_md": "> **Samagra ID Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the official website: [samagra.gov.in](https://samagra.gov.in/).\n**Step 2:** Click on the option “Register Family” or “Register Member”.\n**Step 3:** Enter the Aadhaar number and other required information.\n**Step 4:** Enter the OTP received on the registered mobile number.\n**Step 5:** Carefully fill in all the required details and upload the necessary documents.\n**Step 6:** Enter the captcha code and click on “Submit Application.”\n> **Offline Samagra ID Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the nearest Lok Seva Kendra, MP Online Kiosk, or Common Service Center (CSC).\n**Step 2:** Provide the required documents and necessary information to complete the registration process.\n> **After Samagra Registration:**\n\n**Step 1:** The interested applicant downloads the [application form](https://transport.mp.gov.in/sites/default/files/documents/yojna_20150001.pdf) (Page No. 10) from the official website. \n**Step 2:** In the application form, fill in all the mandatory fields, and attach copies of all the mandatory documents (self-attest, if required).\n**Step 3:** Submit the duly filled and signed application form along with the documents to the District or Regional Transport Office.\n<br>\n\n"
        }
