      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant should be a permanent resident of Madhya Pradesh.\n1. The applicant should be a registered transport vehicle driver or conductor.\n1. The applicant should possess a valid commercial driving license or conductor&#39;s license issued in Madhya Pradesh.\n1. The applicant’s name should be registered on the Samagra Portal.\n1. The applicant should be actively engaged or registered as a transport driver or conductor.\n1. The applicant should not be a government employee.\n\n<br>\n\n",
